  "text": "We have recently reported a case in which there was transformation of pulmonary nodules into pulmonary cysts in a 40-year-old woman who was a non-cigarette smoker with multi-metastatic pulmonary adenocarcinoma, an EML4-ALK gene rearrangement, and who was successfully treated with crizotinib [CITATION_1] .",
